<subSubSection pageId="53" pageNumber="182" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="53.[169,1375,738,1161]" pageId="53" pageNumber="182">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[170,525,1010,1043]" pageId="53" pageNumber="182">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
The Pantepui Slender Opossum has not been assessed on The IUCN Red List because it was described very recently. Conservation status of all opossumsis being reassessed by the IUCN New World Marsupial Specialists Group.
</paragraph>
